<h1>Verify your email</h1>
<p>Hi <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>Thanks for signing up for <strong>{{appName}}</strong>. Enter this 6-digit code in the app to complete registration:</p>

<span class="label">Verification code</span>
<div class="code-box">{{code}}</div>

<div class="surface surface-primary">
  <p><strong>Expires in 24 hours.</strong> Do not share this code with anyone.</p>
</div>

<p class="muted" style="margin-top: 16px;">If you did not create an account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
